Title: Coma
Plot: Albert determines that neither Leo nor Jaqcues killed Laura, but he is unable find any leads into who shot Cooper. Cooper says they must find the third man, who he believes to be Bob, the grey haird man.  Albert reports that Cooper's ex-partner, Windom Earle, escaped from an insane asylum.  Ben Horne can't decide which of the mill ledgers to destroy.  The Log Lady tells Major Briggs to deliver a message to Agent Cooper.  An Asian man spies on Cooper.  Shelly visits Leo in the hospital.
